  {
    "id": "kp-5.2-02",
    "section": "5.2",
    "order": 2,
    "title": "Enlargements",
    "title_zh": "位似变换 (放大与缩小)",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "An **enlargement** changes the size of a shape but keeps it similar (angles remain the same). It is defined by a **center of enlargement** and a **scale factor** $k$.\n\n**Positive scale factor** ($k > 1$): The shape gets larger and moves further from the center.\n**Fractional scale factor** ($0 < k < 1$): The shape gets smaller (it is a reduction).\n**Negative scale factor** ($k < 0$): The image appears on the **opposite side** of the center and is **inverted** (rotated $180^\\circ$).\n\nDistance from center to image point $= k \\times$ distance from center to original point.\n\n**Area effect**: If the scale factor is $k$, the area of the image is $k^2 \\times$ the area of the original shape.",
      "zh": "**位似变换**改变图形的大小但保持相似（角度不变）。它由**位似中心**和**比例因子** $k$ 定义。\n\n**正比例因子** ($k > 1$)：图形变大并远离中心。\n**分比例因子** ($0 < k < 1$)：图形变小（缩小）。\n**负比例因子** ($k < 0$)：像出现在中心的**另一侧**，并且是**倒立的**（旋转了 $180^\\circ$）。\n\n中心到像点的距离 $= k \\times$ 中心到原点的距离。\n\n**面积效应**：如果比例因子是 $k$，则像的面积是原图形面积的 $k^2$ 倍。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-describe-enlarge",
        "label": "Describe an enlargement",
        "label_zh": "描述位似变换",
        "description": "State the center of enlargement and the scale factor.",
        "description_zh": "指出位似中心和比例因子。"
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-negative-sf",
        "label": "Enlargement with negative scale factor",
        "label_zh": "负比例因子的位似变换",
        "description": "Perform or describe an enlargement where $k$ is negative.",
        "description_zh": "执行或描述 $k$ 为负数的位似变换。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-describe-enlarge",
        "question": "Triangle T has vertices $(2,2), (2,4), (5,2)$. It is enlarged with center $(0,0)$ and scale factor $3$. Find the coordinates of the new vertices.",
        "question_zh": "三角形 T 的顶点为 $(2,2), (2,4), (5,2)$。以 $(0,0)$ 为中心，比例因子为 $3$ 进行位似变换。求新顶点的坐标。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Since the center is $(0,0)$, multiply each coordinate by the scale factor $k=3$.\n**Step 2:** Calculate new coordinates:\n$(2, 2) \\rightarrow (2 \\times 3, 2 \\times 3) = (6, 6)$\n$(2, 4) \\rightarrow (2 \\times 3, 4 \\times 3) = (6, 12)$\n$(5, 2) \\rightarrow (5 \\times 3, 2 \\times 3) = (15, 6)$\n**Answer:** $(6,6), (6,12), (15,6)$.",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 由于中心是 $(0,0)$，将每个坐标乘以比例因子 $k=3$。\n**步骤2：** 计算新坐标：\n$(2, 2) \\rightarrow (2 \\times 3, 2 \\times 3) = (6, 6)$\n$(2, 4) \\rightarrow (2 \\times 3, 4 \\times 3) = (6, 12)$\n$(5, 2) \\rightarrow (5 \\times 3, 2 \\times 3) = (15, 6)$\n**答案：** $(6,6), (6,12), (15,6)$。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/1H/June/2022"
      },
      {
        "patternId": "ep-negative-sf",
        "question": "Shape A is enlarged by scale factor $-2$ with center $(1,1)$. If a point on A is $(3,2)$, where is its image?",
        "question_zh": "图形 A 以 $(1,1)$ 为中心，比例因子为 $-2$ 进行位似变换。如果 A 上的一点是 $(3,2)$，它的像在哪里？",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Find the vector from the center $(1,1)$ to the point $(3,2)$.\nVector $= \\begin{pmatrix} 3-1 \\\\ 2-1 \\end{pmatrix} = \\begin{pmatrix} 2 \\\\ 1 \\end{pmatrix}$.\n**Step 2:** Multiply this vector by the scale factor $k = -2$.\nNew vector $= -2 \\times \\begin{pmatrix} 2 \\\\ 1 \\end{pmatrix} = \\begin{pmatrix} -4 \\\\ -2 \\end{pmatrix}$.\n**Step 3:** Add this new vector to the center $(1,1)$.\nImage position $= (1 + (-4), 1 + (-2)) = (-3, -1)$.\n**Answer:** $(-3, -1)$.",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 找到从中心 $(1,1)$ 到点 $(3,2)$ 的向量。\n向量 $= \\begin{pmatrix} 3-1 \\\\ 2-1 \\end{pmatrix} = \\begin{pmatrix} 2 \\\\ 1 \\end{pmatrix}$。\n**步骤2：** 将此向量乘以比例因子 $k = -2$。\n新向量 $= -2 \\times \\begin{pmatrix} 2 \\\\ 1 \\end{pmatrix} = \\begin{pmatrix} -4 \\\\ -2 \\end{pmatrix}$。\n**步骤3：** 将新向量加到中心 $(1,1)$ 上。\n像的位置 $= (1 + (-4), 1 + (-2)) = (-3, -1)$。\n**答案：** $(-3, -1)$。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/2H/Jan/2021"
      }
    ],
